high_descs: Walk around the left side of the couch to face the left side of the living room table.
Pick up the watch on the living room table.
Walk past the right side of the couch and turn left to face the end of the table.
Put the watch on the plate on the table.
Pick up the plate with a watch on it on the table.
Walk straight past the left side of the table and turn left to face a black end table.
Place the plate with a watch on it on the black end table.
anns.task_desc: Place a watch on a plate as well as place it on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn left then right to go around the sofa and face the end of the glass coffee table.
Pick up the watch off of the coffee table.
Turn around then go to the left then to the left again to face the end of the glass dining table.
Place the watch on the white plate.
Pick up the plate with the watch on it.
Turn left then right to walk behind the sofa and face the end of the black lamp table.
Place the white dish on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place the white dish with the watch on it on the black lamp table.

high_descs: Walk to the glass coffee table.
Grab the watch off the table.
Walk to the edge of the dining table.
Place the watch on the plate.
Grab the plate with the watch on it.
Walk to the small table in front of the curtains.
Place the plate and watch on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a watch on a plate to present it on a table.
